snippet.title: ParallaxNick
snippet.description:
A channel for the sharing of knowledge of science, history and the multiverse at large. I look to the past to place our present understanding in context, and, I hope, better grasp the future. 

Follow the conversation at my Twitter:
https://twitter.com/nickrwebb?lang=en-gb

or join the Facebook group:
https://www.facebook.com/groups/307258169803345/
